data.description: It is hard to captures this versatile home’s charm and space in photos! THIS HOUSE IS A MUST SEE!!! This lovely brick home sits on TWO lots  (ONLY 1 HOA FEE) and has TWO sperate driveways: making great for multiple cars, multi-generational families, working from home and anyone with a trailer or recreational vehicles. This immaculately kept home is all brick, has 3-bedrooms and 3-FULL bathrooms PLUS a BONUS ROOM (currently used as a 4th bedroom) would also be great as a mancave/mother-in-law suite/ office/ gym/ playroom or an additional bedroom. This room (that has a built-in closet) is downstairs, has a full bathroom, and a private exterior entrance! On the main level, the master bedroom has it’s own private bathroom suite and an entrance to the sunroom for enjoying your morning coffee and watching birds in the private wooded backyard. The living area in this home is super flexible! The original floorplan has a Den off the kitchen and a Living Room/Dining Room combo at the front of the house. The Den has beautiful wood burning fireplace and is currently used as Hearth Room/Dining Room, with the entire length of the front room is set up as living space. All living areas have Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring, including the spacious kitchen. The bedrooms all have carpet, and there is new paint throughout. The 2-car garage with driveway is located off of Ridgewood and the other driveway is located in the cul-de-sac on S. Windgate Circle. This home has a low maintenance yard, and greenhouse storage located under the sunroom, and is close to the Ridgewood pool and playground. Conveniently located near I-10, shopping (4-5 minutes from Hwy 90!), restaurants and movie theaters.
